article_title: Study: West Virginia had greatest drop in uninsured
article_text:
Huntington, WV (25701)

Today

Partly cloudy this morning, then becoming cloudy during the afternoon. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High 83F. Winds SW at 5 to 10 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy skies. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low around 65F. Winds light and variable.

article_metadata.author: The Associated Press

og.description: CHARLESTON — Federal data shows West Virginia had the greatest percentage drop among the states over a two-year period for adults without health insurance.
